  "description": {
    "zh": "你好啊，老兄，帮我个忙吧。我今天派了一些弟兄去Ultra收集布料，但是一大堆PMC给了他们一个“温暖的欢迎仪式”，朝我的兄弟们肆意开火，把他们赶出了商场。我可是在这里做生意的啊，对吧！老兄，麻烦你去解决掉这些烦人的家伙。算我欠你个人情！",
    "en": "Salam, brother, help me out. I sent my guys to Ultra today to grab some clothes, but a big group of PMCs gave them a \"warm welcome\" - fucking shot at my guys and kicked them out of the mall. I'm running a damn business here, mind you! Need to make deliveries, people are waiting. Brother, please go and deal with those fuckers. I'll owe you big!"
  },
